ge/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"chip","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSChip"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllChipComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ChipComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"chip","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chip"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") , spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and border  (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider/chipColorContentDisabled":{"kind":"symbol","title":"chipColorContentDisabled","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemechipcomponenttokensprovider\/chipcolorcontentdisabled","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeChipComponentTokensProvider\/chipColorContentDisabled","role":"symbol","abstract":[],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"chipColorContentDisabled","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticTokens","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"}}}